               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270215-219-person1180">
                  WILLIAM 
                  BIDGOOD
               <interp inst="t18270215-219-person1180" type="surname" value="BIDGOOD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270215-219-person1180" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270215-219-person1180" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in Oxford-street, and saw the prisoner and another trying to get this cloak - I waited opposite, and at last saw the prisoner take it from within the door - I went, and took him - he threw it into a door-way.</p>
